text.tspan: Save raw data from accouts, transactions, account statements.
ABT: Analytics Base Table (cols=feats, rows=points, last col=label)
Model: Prediction model that was trained on ABT
FeatureList: Describes ABT structure so that columns can be recreated with new data
Err: Estimated prediction error of model
ABT*: An ABT derived from data, but which might have different features and therefore doesnt fit to Model
FeatureList*: Describes ABT*. Together with FeatureList ABT can be created from ABT*
Transactions: Transactions table in a normalized format
Transactions*: Transactions table before user made changes (regarding account information)
